        "created_at": "2025-02-06T14:58:36.972Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"vvxrtues\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"66620\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/v/c77e96/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> vvxrtues:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>make it an option if you prefer not to use those</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>sounds to me essentially like this request</p><aside class=\"quote quote-modified\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"20333\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/v/45deac/48.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/customizable-swipe-actions-on-conversation-list/20333\">Customizable swipe actions on conversation list</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/android-feature-requests/18\"><span data-category-id=\"18\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #2D8B39; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF; --parent-category-badge-color: #83B72A;\" data-parent-category-id=\"17\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --has-parent\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Android Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    I see the right swipe action on a conversation will archive it. \n <a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/2X/d/d78f2bbfbc077e610dee6568ab2fa77b64910e28.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/d78f2bbfbc077e610dee6568ab2fa77b64910e28\" title=\"\">[image]</a> \nHow about delete instead of archive? \nor maybe right swipe - archive, left swipe - delete or vice-versa \nAFAIK, Gmail has such a setting. \nIt is easy to delete many spam SMS using swipe actions to keep the inbox clean. <img width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/mailbox_with_mail.png?v=12\" title=\"mailbox_with_mail\" alt=\"mailbox_with_mail\" class=\"emoji\"><img width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\"sparkles\" alt=\"sparkles\" class=\"emoji\"> \nGot this idea suggestion, so thought of sharing it here to read more views on this. <img width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/slightly_smiling_face.png?v=12\" title=\"slightly_smiling_face\" alt=\"slightly_smiling_face\" class=\"emoji\"> \nThanks.\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n",
